        "gg2Qn3hJVgP_text": "<p>Proven Results While You Sleep</p>",
        "gg3BajX3jAe_text": "<p>I absolutely love that refreshing, cooling feeling in my routine — and this <strong>Salmon PDRN</strong> mask nails it. You get that calming, spa-like effect right at home while it <strong>soothes</strong>, <strong>deeply hydrates</strong>, and <strong>boosts collagen</strong> for a <strong>smoother, firmer, radiant</strong> glow. Such a simple, luxurious way to unwind and truly care for your skin. If you haven’t tried it yet, you’re in for a treat!</p>",
        "gg5jhvAeOg-_text": "<p>Try It for 60 Days, Totally Risk-Free</p>",
