        "gg7_objrOEc_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-71051f67-8e75-4fa8-b548-3d16cd73cd7a.png",
        "gg8Tjx0drcK_label": "<p><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;font-size:13px;\"><strong>Check availability</strong></span></p>",
        "gg8qbjp2nD2_text": "<p>No Irritation for Sensitive Skin</p>",
        "gg9IIKcaXL6_label": "<p><span style=\"color:#FFFFFF;font-size:13px;\"><strong>Check availability</strong></span></p>",
        "ggFYCvYdkkz_text": "Are you finally ready to give your skin the renewal it deserves? 💕&nbsp;",
        "ggHIzq54zz__text": "5. Celebrity-Favorite",
        "ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-27b150b2-4d34-4a80-a224-740e5f9bc8f3.png",
        "ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-46ddba81-6c7e-441b-b2d1-edeebc781354.jpg",
        "ggIu24cKJ2N_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-27b150b2-4d34-4a80-a224-740e5f9bc8f3.png",
        "ggL99cbnlZo_text": "<p>GUARANTEED: In just a couple of hours, the Nifora facial mask makes your skin glow so brightly you won’t believe your mirror. If you think you've surpassed Korean beauty standards with just one application, you’re right. This is what Nifora can do for you every time you use it.</p>",
        "ggMTtLiPXuX_text": "<p>By Molly Richards<br>Last Updated September, 24 2025</p>",
        "ggN-h1PmvDV_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/For_LP_9.png",
        "ggNzvrSfCrV_text": "2. Scientifically Proven Ingredients",
        "ggOGc25WEdF_text": "<p>We’ve got a <strong>limited-time offer</strong> just for you. I’m confident you’ll love the <strong>Salmon PDRN Collagen Mask</strong> — it helps <strong>repair, firm, and brighten</strong> your skin for that radiant, youthful glow. And the best part? It’s <strong>100% risk-free for 60 days</strong>. If you’re not amazed by your results, we’ll refund you — no questions asked. 💕<br>It’s time to experience the glow your skin deserves!</p>",
        "ggOkzpODfF8_text": "6.&nbsp;Cooling &amp; Soothing Effect",
        "ggQ78Sg6Zrx_text": "<p>When I hear something’s a celebrity favorite, I have to try it — and after using the <strong>Salmon PDRN Collagen Mask</strong>, I totally get the hype. It’s not just the clean formula; it’s the results. <strong>Salmon PDRN</strong> helps <strong>repair</strong> and <strong>boost collagen</strong>, so my skin looks <strong>smoother, firmer, and brighter</strong> with that flawless, youthful glow. If it works for them, it definitely works for us.</p>",
        "ggQPtwZzMvG_text": "4. Sensitive Skin Friendly",
        "ggTCZJLSmNN_text": "7. Exclusive Summer Sale is now Live!",
        "ggUMmUh3HgV_label": "<p>Shop Now</p>",
        "ggUYRw8nmHu_text": "<strong>Discover why 40,000+ women</strong> trust the <strong>Salmon PDRN Collagen Mask</strong> — it repairs, firms, and brightens to reveal visibly smoother, youthful, radiant skin.",
        "ggUrpHf4v9e_text": "<p>Infused with <strong>Salmon PDRN (polynucleotides)</strong>, this advanced formula goes beyond surface moisture to <strong>revitalize skin from within</strong>. The bioactive molecules help <strong>restore hydration balance</strong>, strengthen the skin barrier, and improve elasticity for a smoother, plumper look. Unlike ordinary masks, it locks in moisture at the cellular level — leaving your skin <strong>deeply hydrated, supple, and glowing</strong> long after you remove it.</p>",
        "ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-ead342dd-6162-44aa-9cec-ffd056a84b84.webp",
        "ggYy6grbLeA_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/gempages_560737037540394069-ead342dd-6162-44aa-9cec-ffd056a84b84.webp",
