        "ggvDN5djePx_text": "<p>Who says youthful, radiant skin has to come from pricey treatments? The <strong>Salmon PDRN Collagen Mask</strong> helps <strong>repair, firm, and brighten</strong> your skin from within — boosting collagen, refining pores, and restoring that healthy glow. Get visible results that feel luxurious, <strong>without the luxury price tag.</strong></p>",
        "ggw6GWQLv30_text": "<p>1 - 2 applications a week - instant results</p>",
        "ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_desktop_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/103b8aa6cbf231bfc714536afca72b00.jpg",
        "ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_mobile_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/103b8aa6cbf231bfc714536afca72b00.jpg",
        "ggxK_8Xcm8n_srcSet_tablet_src": "https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/0798/4028/0923/files/103b8aa6cbf231bfc714536afca72b00.jpg",
        "ggxpEEAWkOo_text": "<p>If you have sensitive skin like me, finding something gentle yet truly effective can be tough. That’s why I love this mask — it’s powered by <strong>Salmon PDRN</strong>, known for its ability to <strong>repair and strengthen</strong> the skin barrier while keeping it calm and hydrated. It helps <strong>soothe irritation</strong>, <strong>boost collagen</strong>, and <strong>restore elasticity</strong>, giving even the most delicate skin a <strong>smooth, radiant glow</strong> without any redness or discomfort. It’s the kind of gentle care that actually transforms your skin.</p>",
        "ggxwUzin72S_text": "<p>Our mask harnesses the power of <strong>Salmon DNA (PDRN)</strong>—rich in polynucleotides—to <strong>stimulate skin cell regeneration</strong>. This renewal process helps <strong>enhance elasticity</strong>, <strong>reduce the look of fine lines</strong>, and <strong>restore a youthful, radiant appearance</strong>.</p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><strong>PDRN</strong>, derived from Salmon DNA, is renowned for its <strong>regenerative</strong> and <strong>repairing</strong> properties. Studies associate it with improved <strong>skin texture and tone</strong>, making it a trusted active in <strong>advanced, results-driven skincare</strong>.</p>"
